Package: libvaladate-1.0-dbg
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Depends:
 libvaladate-1.0-0 (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: Debugging symbols for Unit testing framework for GObject-based code - library
 Valadate is a unit testing framework based on GLib Testing. It is primarily
 intended for testing code written in Vala, but can be used with any
 GObject-based code.

